# put urls of interesting products here.
# please take care to add a newline after last line.
#
# format: play.com_url TAB maximum_price/previous_price NEWLINE
#
# maximum_price if automatically updated to currect price, if it drops (but not if it rises).  so you keep on geting notifications whenever price drops.
#
# if you omit the maximum/previous price, we automatically fetch&save the _current_ product price on next run.  afters, you get a notification whenever the price drops below the previous price.
# 
# include the cur query parameter to ensure correct currency is used, see the examples
# 257 = £
# 258 = €
# 
